      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Great value for someone looking for a solid, usable car without paying top-tier money. This one is in fair overall condition with honest wear consistent with age and use, but it still has plenty to offer as a dependable driver or a car to improve over time. A straightforward, budget-friendly option with good potential for the next owner.",
