      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for cheap wheels that can still get the job done? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest budget-friendly option with plenty of life left for the right buyer. Great for a runabout, first project, or something to keep you moving without spending a fortune. If you know your way around cars or just need affordable transportation, this could be a smart buy. Priced to sell and worth a look.",
      "price": 5800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly project with a strong mechanical feel and plenty of upside for the next owner. The engine pulls cleanly, the drivetrain feels intact, and it has the kind of honest, usable character enthusiasts look for in a fixer-upper rather than a stripped-out parts car. A great candidate for someone who wants dependable basic transportation now and a platform to sort, refresh, and improve over time. Priced to move, but with enough substance to justify a serious look.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Cheap. Runs. Gets you from A to B. Rough around the edges, priced to move fast. Solid deal for a budget buyer.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is the kind of car that still turns heads for all the right reasons: full of personality, presence, and untapped potential. It has the sort of lived-in charm that makes every drive feel a little more authentic, whether you're looking for a budget-friendly daily, a hands-on project, or a vehicle with real character instead of cookie-cutter sameness. A great opportunity for someone who sees value in solid style and possibility.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
